Vlad Dascalu is on a heater right now!🔥

After winning a European Championship in late June, he took third in Val di Sole for his first podium of the year. There’s no question that he’s rounding into form. The season also admittedly didn’t start as he had hoped. He only cracked the top 10 in a World Cup race once before last Sunday. Compare that to 2022, when he was top 10 in all seven of the first World Cup races he completed.

Could we see the Romanian force work his way up the rankings in the second half of the season?🇷🇴

I was really looking forward to representing Romania for the Olympic test event in Paris. But after the World Cup in Les Gets I became sick and didn’t recover as fast as I would have liked.
